---
title: Sweet Orange-Glazed Lamb with Baby Broccoli & Cheesy Mash
description: Sweet and zesty oranges don’t have to be saved for desserts, bring in the juicy fruit flavours to a seared lamb dinner by making
an orange glaze. The savoury side is covered with cheesy potato mash and garlicky greens.
